long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Every time you open a new tab in your Chrome browser, we’ll show you a randomly selected project from Archilovers.com network.
You can easily click on the picture to see more information about the project.
If you want see more projects you can click on the shuffle icon on the top right of the screen.

Transform your “New Tab” page into a inspiring tools!
